---
// ── 頁面介紹（可直接修改這段文字）──
const pageDesc = "當下心情的配樂，以及聽這首歌時想說的話。";

import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";

const allMusic = (await getCollection("music")).sort(
    (a, b) => b.data.pubDate.valueOf() - a.data.pubDate.valueOf(),
);

const artists = [...new Set(allMusic.map((p) => p.data.artist || "佚名"))].sort();

const groupedMusic = allMusic.reduce((acc, post) => {
    const d = post.data.pubDate;
    const key = `${d.getFullYear()}-${String(d.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, "0")}`;
    if (!acc[key]) acc[key] = { year: d.getFullYear(), month: d.getMonth() + 1, posts: [] as typeof allMusic };
    acc[key].posts.push(post);
    return acc;
}, {} as Record<string, { year: number; month: number; posts: typeof allMusic }>);

const musicGroups = Object.entries(groupedMusic)
    .sort(([a], [b]) => b.localeCompare(a))
    .map(([key, val]) => ({ key, ...val }));
---

<Layout title="拾音集 | 樂評編目 - Bruce">
    <div class="paper-texture"></div>

    <main class="music-archive">
        <header class="archive-header">
            <div class="header-row">
                <h1>拾音集 <small>SOUND & TRACKS</small></h1>
                <p class="page-desc">{pageDesc}</p>
                <div class="archive-filter">
                    <label for="artist-select" class="filter-label">FILTER</label>
                    <div class="select-wrapper">
                        <select id="artist-select" class="filter-select">
                            <option value="all">全部 ALL</option>
                            {artists.map((artist) => (
                                <option value={artist}>{artist}</option>
                            ))}
                        </select>
                        <span class="select-arrow">↓</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="header-line"></div>
        </header>

        <div id="music-grid">
            {musicGroups.map((group) => (
                <section class="date-group" data-group={group.key}>
                    <div class="group-header">
                        <span class="group-year">{group.year} 年</span>
                        <span class="group-month">{group.month} 月</span>
                        <div class="group-line"></div>
                        <span class="group-count">{group.posts.length} TRACKS</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mc-grid">
                        {group.posts.map((post) => (
                            <a
                                href={`/music/${post.id}`}
                                class="mc-card"
                                data-artist={post.data.artist || "佚名"}
                                data-youtube-id={post.data.youtubeId || ""}
                                data-song-name={post.data.songName || ""}
                            >
                                <div class="mc-cover">
                                    {post.data.youtubeId
                                        ? <img class="mc-thumb" src={`https://img.youtube.com/vi/${post.data.youtubeId}/hqdefault.jpg`} alt={post.data.songName} loading="lazy" />
                                        : <div class="mc-thumb-placeholder"><span>{post.data.artist}</span></div>
                                    }
                                    {post.data.youtubeId && (
                                        <div class="mc-yt-wrapper">
                                            <div class="mc-yt-target"></div>
                                        </div>
                                    )}
                                    <div class="mc-hover-overlay">
                                        <span class="mc-play-icon">▶</span>
                                        <span class="mc-hover-hint">懸停播放</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <span class="mc-artist-badge">{post.data.artist}</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mc-info">
                                    <h3 class="mc-songname">《{post.data.songName}》</h3>
                                    <p class="mc-desc">{post.data.title}</p>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        ))}
                    </div>
                </section>
            ))}
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- 底部迷你播放器 -->
    <div id="mini-player" class="mini-player">
        <div class="mp-info">
            <span class="mp-song" id="mp-song"></span>
            <span class="mp-artist" id="mp-artist"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="mp-controls">
            <button id="mp-playpause" class="mp-btn mp-playpause">⏸</button>
            <div class="mp-progress-area">
                <span class="mp-time" id="mp-cur">0:00</span>
                <input type="range" id="mp-bar" class="mp-bar" min="0" max="1000" value="0" step="1">
                <span class="mp-time" id="mp-dur">0:00</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button id="mp-close" class="mp-btn mp-close-btn">✕</button>
    </div>
</Layout>

<script is:inline>
    // ── YouTube IFrame API 初始化 ──────────────────────────────────────
    if (!window.__ytApiListenerSet) {
        window.__ytApiListenerSet = true;
        window.onYouTubeIframeAPIReady = function () { window.ytApiReady = true; };
    }
    if (!document.querySelector('script[src*="youtube.com/iframe_api"]')) {
        var s = document.createElement('script');
        s.src = 'https://www.youtube.com/iframe_api';
        document.head.appendChild(s);
    }
    if (window.YT && window.YT.Player) window.ytApiReady = true;

    // ── 全域清理參考（頁面切換用）────────────────────────────────────
    if (!window.__musicCleanupSet) {
        window.__musicCleanupSet = true;
        document.addEventListener('astro:before-preparation', function () {
            if (window.__musicStop) { window.__musicStop(); window.__musicStop = null; }
        });
    }

    // ── 主邏輯 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    function musicSetup() {
        var ytPlayer    = null;
        var activeCard  = null;
        var pollTimer   = null;
        var isDragging  = false;
        var switchTimer = null;   // 3 秒切歌防抖

        var miniPlayer  = document.getElementById('mini-player');
        var mpPlayPause = document.getElementById('mp-playpause');
        var mpClose     = document.getElementById('mp-close');
        var mpBar       = document.getElementById('mp-bar');
        var mpCur       = document.getElementById('mp-cur');
        var mpDur       = document.getElementById('mp-dur');
        var mpSong      = document.getElementById('mp-song');
        var mpArtist    = document.getElementById('mp-artist');

        if (!miniPlayer) return;

        // ── 工具函式 ──
        function fmt(sec) {
            if (!isFinite(sec) || isNaN(sec)) return '0:00';
            var m = Math.floor(sec / 60), s = Math.floor(sec % 60);
            return m + ':' + (s < 10 ? '0' : '') + s;
        }

        function fillBar(pct) {
            mpBar.style.background =
                'linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent) ' + pct + '%, rgba(255,255,255,0.18) ' + pct + '%)';
        }

        function tick() {
            if (!ytPlayer || !ytPlayer.getCurrentTime || isDragging) return;
            try {
                var cur = ytPlayer.getCurrentTime();
                var dur = ytPlayer.getDuration();
                if (!dur) return;
                var pct = (cur / dur) * 100;
                mpBar.value = Math.round((cur / dur) * 1000);
                mpCur.textContent = fmt(cur);
                mpDur.textContent = fmt(dur);
                fillBar(pct);
            } catch (_) {}
        }

        // ── 停止清理 ──
        function stopPlayer() {
            if (pollTimer)  { clearInterval(pollTimer); pollTimer = null; }
            if (ytPlayer)   { try { ytPlayer.destroy(); } catch (_) {} ytPlayer = null; }
            if (activeCard) { activeCard.classList.remove('active'); activeCard = null; }
            if (miniPlayer) miniPlayer.classList.remove('active');
            mpBar.value = 0;
            fillBar(0);
        }
        window.__musicStop = stopPlayer;

        // ── 建立播放器 ──
        function createPlayer(card, ytId) {
            var wrapper = card.querySelector('.mc-yt-wrapper');
            if (!wrapper) return;

            // 清除舊 iframe，重新插入 target div
            wrapper.innerHTML = '';
            var target = document.createElement('div');
            wrapper.appendChild(target);

            ytPlayer = new YT.Player(target, {
                videoId: ytId,
                playerVars: { autoplay: 1, controls: 0, loop: 1, playlist: ytId, playsinline: 1, rel: 0, modestbranding: 1 },
                events: {
                    onReady: function (e) {
                        e.target.playVideo();

                        // 把 YT 建立的 iframe 撐滿 wrapper
                        var iframe = wrapper.querySelector('iframe');
                        if (iframe) {
                            iframe.style.position    = 'absolute';
                            iframe.style.top         = '0';
                            iframe.style.left        = '0';
                            iframe.style.width       = '100%';
                            iframe.style.height      = '100%';
                            iframe.style.border      = 'none';
                            iframe.style.pointerEvents = 'none';
                        }

                        card.classList.add('active');

                        // 更新 mini player
                        mpSong.textContent   = '《' + (card.dataset.songName || '') + '》';
                        mpArtist.textContent = card.dataset.artist || '';
                        mpPlayPause.textContent = '⏸';
                        mpDur.textContent    = fmt(e.target.getDuration());
                        miniPlayer.classList.add('active');

                        if (pollTimer) clearInterval(pollTimer);
                        pollTimer = setInterval(tick, 250);
                    },
                    onStateChange: function (e) {
                        // YT.PlayerState: 1=playing, 2=paused, 0=ended
                        if (e.data === 1)      mpPlayPause.textContent = '⏸';
                        else if (e.data === 2) mpPlayPause.textContent = '▶';
                        else if (e.data === 0) mpPlayPause.textContent = '▶';
                    }
                }
            });
        }

        // ── 切換到指定卡片 ──
        function activateCard(card) {
            if (activeCard === card) return;

            if (pollTimer)  { clearInterval(pollTimer); pollTimer = null; }
            if (ytPlayer)   { try { ytPlayer.destroy(); } catch (_) {} ytPlayer = null; }
            if (activeCard) { activeCard.classList.remove('active'); }

            activeCard = card;
            var ytId = card.dataset.youtubeId;

            if (window.ytApiReady) {
                createPlayer(card, ytId);
            } else {
                // API 尚未就緒，輪詢等待
                var wait = setInterval(function () {
                    if (window.ytApiReady) { clearInterval(wait); createPlayer(card, ytId); }
                }, 80);
            }
        }

        // ── 歌手篩選 ──
        var select = document.getElementById('artist-select');
        if (select) {
            select.addEventListener('change', function () {
                var val = select.value;
                document.querySelectorAll('.date-group').forEach(function (section) {
                    var count = 0;
                    section.querySelectorAll('.mc-card').forEach(function (card) {
                        if (val === 'all' || card.dataset.artist === val) {
                            card.style.display = ''; count++;
                        } else {
                            card.style.display = 'none';
                        }
                    });
                    section.style.display = count === 0 ? 'none' : '';
                });
            });
        }

        // ── 卡片懸停（正在播音樂時，移到其他卡片需等 3 秒才切換）──
        document.querySelectorAll('.mc-card').forEach(function (card) {
            if (!card.dataset.youtubeId) return;

            card.addEventListener('mouseenter', function () {
                clearTimeout(switchTimer);
                if (activeCard === card) return;        // 已在播這首，不動作
                if (activeCard) {
                    // 有其他歌在播：延遲 3 秒才切換
                    switchTimer = setTimeout(function () { activateCard(card); }, 1500);
                } else {
                    // 沒有歌在播：立即開始
                    activateCard(card);
                }
            });

            card.addEventListener('mouseleave', function () {
                clearTimeout(switchTimer);  // 離開卡片就取消預約切換
            });
        });

        // ── 播放 / 暫停 ──
        mpPlayPause.addEventListener('click', function () {
            if (!ytPlayer) return;
            var state = ytPlayer.getPlayerState();
            if (state === 1) ytPlayer.pauseVideo();
            else             ytPlayer.playVideo();
        });

        // ── 關閉 ──
        mpClose.addEventListener('click', stopPlayer);

        // ── 進度條拖拉 ──
        mpBar.addEventListener('mousedown',  function () { isDragging = true; });
        mpBar.addEventListener('touchstart', function () { isDragging = true; }, { passive: true });

        mpBar.addEventListener('input', function () {
            if (!ytPlayer) return;
            var dur = ytPlayer.getDuration();
            var cur = (mpBar.value / 1000) * dur;
            mpCur.textContent = fmt(cur);
            fillBar((mpBar.value / 1000) * 100);
        });

        function commitSeek() {
            isDragging = false;
            if (!ytPlayer) return;
            var dur = ytPlayer.getDuration();
            ytPlayer.seekTo((mpBar.value / 1000) * dur, true);
        }
        mpBar.addEventListener('mouseup',  commitSeek);
        mpBar.addEventListener('touchend', commitSeek);
    }

    document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', musicSetup);
</script>

<style>
    .music-archive {
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: "Noto Serif TC", serif;
    }

    /* ── Header ── */
    .header-row { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .archive-header h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin: 0; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -1.5px; }
    .archive-header h1 small { font-size: 0.75rem; font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; margin-left: 0.6rem; }
    .header-line { width: 100%; height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem; position: relative; }
    .header-line::after { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: -1px; width: 80px; height: 3px; background: var(--accent); }

    .page-desc {
        flex: 1;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin: 0 0 0.15rem 0;
        font-style: italic;
        padding-left: 2rem;
        border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
        min-width: 120px;
    }

    /* ── Filter ── */
    .archive-filter { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; padding-bottom: 0.15rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .filter-label { font-size: 0.6rem; font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; white-space: nowrap; }
    .select-wrapper { position: relative; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; }
    .filter-select { appearance: none; -webkit-appearance: none; background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 3px; padding: 0.3rem 1.8rem 0.3rem 0.7rem; font-size: 0.78rem; font-family: "Noto Serif TC", serif; color: var(--ink); cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.3s, color 0.3s; min-width: 160px; }
    .filter-select:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--accent); }
    .filter-select:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
    .select-arrow { position: absolute; right: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--muted); pointer-events: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
    .select-wrapper:hover .select-arrow { color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── Date group ── */
    .date-group { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .group-header { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
    .group-year { font-size: 0.62rem; font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--muted); }
    .group-month { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .group-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); align-self: center; }
    .group-count { font-size: 0.58rem; font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }

    /* ── Grid ── */
    .mc-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.2rem; }

    /* ── Card ── */
    .mc-card { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s, border-color 0.3s; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    .mc-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(139,69,19,0.1); border-color: var(--accent); }
    .mc-card.active { border-color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── Cover ── */
    .mc-cover { position: relative; height: 190px; overflow: hidden; background: var(--border); }
    .mc-thumb { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.4s; }
    .mc-card.active .mc-thumb { opacity: 0; }
    .mc-thumb-placeholder { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139,69,19,0.08), rgba(139,69,19,0.18)); }
    .mc-thumb-placeholder span { font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; }

    /* ── YouTube wrapper（YT.Player 的目標容器）── */
    .mc-yt-wrapper { position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.45s; z-index: 1; overflow: hidden; }
    .mc-card.active .mc-yt-wrapper { opacity: 1; }

    /* ── Hover overlay ── */
    .mc-hover-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.4rem; background: transparent; transition: background 0.3s; z-index: 2; pointer-events: none; }
    .mc-play-icon { font-size: 2rem; color: #fff; opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.8); transition: opacity 0.25s, transform 0.25s; text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
    .mc-hover-hint { font-size: 0.6rem; font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #fff; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.25s; text-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
    .mc-card:hover:not(.active) .mc-hover-overlay { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.18); }
    .mc-card:hover:not(.active) .mc-play-icon { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    .mc-card:hover:not(.active) .mc-hover-hint { opacity: 1; }

    /* ── Artist badge ── */
    .mc-artist-badge { position: absolute; top: 0.6rem; right: 0.6rem; font-size: 0.72rem; font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 700; background: rgba(20,10,5,0.68); color: #fff; z-index: 3; pointer-events: none; backdrop-filter: blur(4px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(4px); }

    /* ── Info ── */
    .mc-info { padding: 0.9rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.3rem; flex: 1; }
    .mc-songname { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; }
    .mc-desc { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden; }

    /* ── Mini Player ── */
    .mini-player {
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 62px;
        background: var(--ink);
        color: var(--paper);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
        transform: translateY(100%);
        transition: transform 0.38s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        z-index: 200;
        border-top: 2px solid var(--accent);
        font-family: "Noto Serif TC", serif;
    }
    .mini-player.active { transform: translateY(0); }

    .mp-info { min-width: 140px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; overflow: hidden; }
    .mp-song { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
    .mp-artist { font-size: 0.6rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; }

    .mp-controls { flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; min-width: 0; }

    .mp-btn { background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: var(--paper); font-size: 1rem; padding: 0; width: 32px; height: 32px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 50%; transition: background 0.2s; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .mp-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
    .mp-close-btn { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .mp-close-btn:hover { color: #fff; }

    .mp-progress-area { flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem; min-width: 0; }
    .mp-time { font-size: 0.62rem; font-family: monospace; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); min-width: 32px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    #mp-cur { text-align: right; }

    /* ── 進度條 ── */
    .mp-bar {
        flex: 1;
        -webkit-appearance: none;
        appearance: none;
        height: 3px;
        border-radius: 3px;
        outline: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
        min-width: 0;
    }
    .mp-bar::-webkit-slider-thumb {
        -webkit-appearance: none;
        width: 13px; height: 13px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--accent);
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: transform 0.15s;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(139,69,19,0.3);
    }
    .mp-bar:hover::-webkit-slider-thumb { transform: scale(1.3); }
    .mp-bar::-moz-range-thumb { width: 13px; height: 13px; border: none; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); cursor: pointer; }
    .mp-bar::-moz-range-track { height: 3px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); border-radius: 3px; }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 850px) { .mc-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
    @media (max-width: 500px) {
        .mc-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .header-top { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
        .page-desc { display: none; }
        .mp-info { display: none; }
    }
</style>
